OL,3,CFive-year-old taught to 'hide in
OL,4,Ctoilet' in case of antisemitic attacks
OL,6,FA mother says her five-year-old son is
OL,7,Fbeing "taught how to hide in the
OL,8,Ftoilets" at his Jewish school incase
OL,9,Fthere is an antisemitic attack.
OL,11,FLucy Salem said her son's school have
OL,12,Falso stocked up on lollies to give to
OL,13,Fchildren incase they need to keep the
OL,14,Fpupils quiet if there is a serious
OL,15,Fthreat.
OL,17,FIt comes after hundreds of antisemitic
OL,18,Fincidents have been recorded in the
OL,19,FNorth West by a Jewish charity.
