OL,6,FThe Community Security Trust says more
OL,7,Fthan 500 incidents took place last
OL,8,Fyear in Greater Manchester, which has
OL,9,Fthe UK's largest Jewish community
OL,10,Foutside London.
OL,12,FLucy Salem said that life as a Jewish
OL,13,Fperson in Greater Manchester is
OL,14,F"terrifying".
OL,16,F"I don't think there's a day that goes
OL,17,Fby that I don't wake up feeling
OL,18,Fanxious. I walk down the street and
OL,19,Fi'm questioning what people are
OL,20,Fthinking and whether they know i'm
OL,21,FJewish."
