OL,6,F"It's just a really sad state of
OL,7,Faffairs and I feel like we're being
OL,8,Ftargeted for something that we are not
OL,9,Fin control of."
OL,11,FShe continued: "I look at my little
OL,12,Fboy and I think 'what kind of a world
OL,13,Fhave I brought you into?' It's not
OL,14,Fsafe.
OL,16,F"At the age of five has been taught
OL,17,Fhow to hide in the toilets at school.
OL,18,FThe fact that they're being taught
OL,19,Fthat makes me feel sick."
