OL,6,FThe Community Security Trust, which
OL,7,Fmonitors anti-Jewish abuse, says there
OL,8,Fwas a sharp rise in incidents of hate
OL,9,Fin the aftermath of the Hamas attacks
OL,10,Fon 7 October and Israel's subsequent
OL,11,Fresponse in Gaza.
OL,13,FIt recorded more than 550 incidents in
OL,14,F2023 in Greater Manchester, which has
OL,15,Fthe UK's largest Jewish community
OL,16,Foutside London.
