OL,6,FMark Levy, Chief Executive of the
OL,7,FJewish Representative Council of
OL,8,FGreater Manchester, said: "What we're
OL,9,Fseeing is Jewish people going about
OL,10,Ftheir daily business in every walk of
OL,11,Flife are being targeted.
OL,13,F"Whether that's children going to and
OL,14,Ffrom school, people at uni , people in
OL,15,Fa theatre, we've had jewish buildings
OL,16,Fbeing defaced with awful graffiti so
OL,17,Fpeople are naturally feeling insecure."
