OL,6,FHe continued: "The anxiety that will
OL,7,Fbe created by the report, which does
OL,8,Fnot shock anyone in our community,
OL,9,Fwill be unprecedented because we have
OL,10,Falways had to endure a surge in hate
OL,11,Fcrime targeting Jewish people when
OL,12,Fthere is a conflict in the Middle
OL,13,FEast."
OL,15,F"But a sheer number of incidents which
OL,16,Fhave taken place since October 7 is
OL,17,Fshocking and has to be utterly
OL,18,Fcondemned."
